These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, cabbage, carrot, lettuce
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, iced-tea, almond-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican, pakistani, russian
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, pink, blue, ivory
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 2. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
 3. the brazilian is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 6. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 7. the mexican is the person eating carrot##1
 8. the person who likes blue is in an even position##4
 9. the person who likes azure is between the person who likes ivory and the person drinking almond-milk##2
10. the person eating banana is the person who likes ivory##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | carrot  | banana    | lettuce    | cabbage   |
| Beverage   | tea     | soy-milk   | iced-tea       | almond-milk    |
| Nationality   | mexican | brazilian | russian    | pakistani |
| Color           | pink | ivory       | azure | blue     |

