.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, zombie, superhero, spy
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, d&b, techno, country
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, cycling, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is the fan of disco##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 6. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the fan of country is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the fan of techno is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of techno is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | sports  | zombie    | superhero     | spy       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Music-Genre   | techno | disco   | d&b   | country    |
| Sport         | cycling | volleyball  | biathlon | climbing   |

