.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, paramedic, social-worker, writer
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, orange, brown, azure
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller, helicopter, trike
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 2. the person who likes orange is the social-worker##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 4. the librarian is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the writer##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who likes azure##1
 8. the writer is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who likes black##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | sprite    | juice      |
| Job           | social-worker | librarian | paramedic | writer     |
| Color   | orange      | azure   | black   | brown |
| Transport           | trike         | quad-bike       | helicopter  | roller       |

