.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, plum, zucchini
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, swisher, aristoff, baccarat
City: nizza, edinburgh, venice, paris
 1. the person drinking fanta is the person eating corn##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 4. the swisher-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person traveling to paris##1
 6. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 9. the person traveling to venice is the swisher-smoker##1
10. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
11. the person drinking sprite is the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | water       | sprite   | fanta   | iced-tea   |
| Food       | lime        | zucchini | corn    | plum       |
| Cigar      | baccarat | swisher    | aristoff  | bolivar |
| City      | edinburgh  | venice  | nizza | paris    |

