.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, orange, pineapple, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku
4 different pets are kept: mouse, hamster, bird, fish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, april, february, october
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person eating spinach##2
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating orange is the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
10. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pineapple    | spinach      | kiwi          | orange    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | sudoku       | rock-climbing | gardening |
| Pet     | fish     | bird      | hamster     | mouse |
| Birthday   | april   | october | february        | september   |

