 3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the dutch##3
 5. the dancer is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the french is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the writer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
10. the egyptian is on the far right##1
11. the project-manager is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
12. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Job   | project-manager | writer    | dancer  | firefighter      |
