The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, bus, skateboard, roller
 1. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the skateboard##2
 3. the american is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
 5. the spanish is on the right of the nigerian##1
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the australian##1
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is between the american and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
11. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
12. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
