.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, mango, potato, strawberry
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, 7up, milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, jazz
4 different games are played: canasta, snooker, scrabble, chess
 1. the person eating mango is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of folk is between the person drinking tea and the person playing snooker##2
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 7. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing chess is the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
11. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of house is on the left of the person eating potato##1
13. the fan of indie is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Food          | garlic     | potato      | strawberry  | mango        |
| Beverage   | tea     | 7up | iced-tea | milk      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | folk        | jazz        | indie        |
| Game         | chess | canasta    | snooker      | scrabble |

