|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Job      | entrepreneur   | analyst   | mechanic     | writer   |
| Birthday   | may  | july       | september | november |
| Pet           | turtle     | goldfish   | ferret     | cat     |
| Sport         | volleyball | ice-hockey | handball   | cycling |

