.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, may, november
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, sports, western
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, canasta, scrabble
 1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Birthday      | may       | october | june        | november        |
| Hobby         | video-games | singing       | card-games | photography |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | satire        | mystery    | sports      |
| Game         | monopoly     | canasta    | scrabble | billiard   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, pop, techno
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, martial-arts, mystery, epic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rugby, water-polo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, sunflower, daffodil, balloon-flower
 1. the fan of techno is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching epic movies##2
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the fan of house is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
 8. the person watching epic movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
10. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4
11. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | ambient | techno     | pop        |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | epic  | martial-arts     | spy |
| Sport         | parkour    | cycling | rugby      | water-polo |
| Flower     | balloon-flower | sunflower     | daffodil | lily       |

 